00:37:26.500 --> 00:37:28.310
that was facing these things.

00:37:28.310 --> 00:37:31.700
Now I don't think the diversity
gap provides all the answers,

00:37:31.700 --> 00:37:35.270
but I do think that it's
asking the right questions.

00:37:35.270 --> 00:37:39.670
So a diversity gap
on the tech field,

00:37:39.670 --> 00:37:45.010
which you see in the lower
