00:42:13.870 --> 00:42:15.470
So what happens next?

00:42:15.470 --> 00:42:17.240
You know, we have all this data.

00:42:17.240 --> 00:42:19.050
I mean, what do we do next?

00:42:19.050 --> 00:42:22.160
And so one thing that we
