01:39:37.750 --> 01:39:41.370 position:56%
That's how much a part of my comfort
zone that summer housing had become.

01:39:41.370 --> 01:39:45.350
I made me feel like New York
was possible and manageable,

01:39:45.350 --> 01:39:48.350
both as an intern and beyond.

01:39:48.350 --> 01:39:52.140
Fortunately, in the past 10
years I have since branched out

01:39:52.140 --> 01:39:54.820
and ridden other trains [laughter].

01:39:54.820 --> 01:39:57.960
So I went back to school.

01:39:57.960 --> 01:40:00.450
I applied to be Scholastic
Children's Defense Fund Fellow,

01:40:00.450 --> 01:40:03.420
for the summers following
my junior and senior years.

01:40:03.420 --> 01:40:06.980
And I participated in the program
for a total of three summers.

01:40:06.980 --> 01:40:10.160
The second summary I was assigned
to Arthur A. Levine Books,

01:40:10.160 --> 01:40:11.820
publisher of Harry Potter.

01:40:11.820 --> 01:40:16.240 position:56%
That was the summer Harry Potter and
the Half Blood Prince was published.

01:40:16.240 --> 01:40:18.810
It's difficult to explain
how incredible being

01:40:18.810 --> 01:40:21.170
at Scholastic for that moment was.

01:40:21.170 --> 01:40:25.970
Our group project that summer was
