01:41:25.750 --> 01:41:28.510
Scholastic's Graphic Novel Imprint,

01:41:28.510 --> 01:41:33.290
which had been established the
year before, and Scholastic Press.

01:41:33.290 --> 01:41:36.050
They were in need of
an editorial assistant.

01:41:36.050 --> 01:41:40.240
So at the end of my third summer
