because I came up fighting a system.

02:50:48.660 --> 02:50:50.800
And you came up now
having to create something.

02:50:50.800 --> 02:50:52.100
Am I making sense?

02:50:52.100 --> 02:50:53.400
&gt;&gt; Kwame Alexander: You are.

02:50:53.400 --> 02:50:54.700
&gt;&gt; Jacqueline Woodson: Yeah.

02:50:54.700 --> 02:50:56.000
&gt;&gt; Nikki Giovanni: And I
