03:11:03.420 --> 03:11:09.460
So in terms of publishing
a book, so publishers --

03:11:09.460 --> 03:11:12.610
mainstream publishers pay you.

03:11:12.610 --> 03:11:16.310
They give you an advance
on signing, and that --

03:11:16.310 --> 03:11:19.660
and what an advance means
is that they'll publish --

03:11:19.660 --> 03:11:22.110
it's a money upfront
and then a whole --

03:11:22.110 --> 03:11:25.180
once those books sell
enough to cover

03:11:25.180 --> 03:11:27.520
that advance then you
start getting royalties.

03:11:27.520 --> 03:11:30.050
Usually 10% escalating to 12%.

03:11:30.050 --> 03:11:34.310
So there's this whole
financial system to it.

03:11:34.310 --> 03:11:35.840
Self-publishing is different.

03:11:35.840 --> 03:11:40.820
Self-publishing you pay to
publish your book and then --

03:11:40.820 --> 03:11:43.850 position:56%
and then all the money that comes --

03:11:43.850 --> 03:11:47.100
that you sell the books
for you earn, right.

03:11:47.100 --> 03:11:48.490
So then you cover -- you put --

03:11:48.490 --> 03:11:51.100
you put up your own advance
and then earn it back.

03:11:51.100 --> 03:11:55.460
And then once you've paid yourself
off from paying for that book all

03:11:55.460 --> 03:11:57.760
that money is money that's yours.

03:11:57.760 --> 03:12:00.190
So there -- some people
self-publish,

03:12:00.190 --> 03:12:03.790
some people go the mainstream
route, some people self-publish

03:12:03.790 --> 03:12:06.110
when the mainstream
doesn't buy their book.

03:12:06.110 --> 03:12:09.110
The thing about the mainstream
is you have a publicist,

03:12:09.110 --> 03:12:12.780
you have an editor, you have a
person who designs your cover.

03:12:12.780 --> 03:12:17.150
You have all of these
people in house that,

03:12:17.150 --> 03:12:18.450
you know, the publisher pays.

03:12:18.450 --> 03:12:21.600
Self-publishing you have to pay
for all that yourself and you have

03:12:21.600 --> 03:12:22.900
to sell the book yourself.

03:12:22.900 --> 03:12:25.440
You know, you have to get
it out there yourself.

03:12:25.440 --> 03:12:27.370
So, does that makes sense?

